Package: bookworm
Title: R interface to Bookworm libraries for text analysis
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person("Benjamin", "Schmidt", email = "bmschmidt@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: R bindings for the Bookworm API, which allows easy access to faceted bag-of-words data on large textual collections. The main function is "bookworm" 
Depends: R (>= 3.1.2)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
Imports: 
    RCurl,
    RJSONIO
Suggests:
    ggplot2,
    tidyr
